Parameters:
tx - Translation in x direction
ty - Translation in y direction
tz - Translation in z direction
q1 - First component of the rotation quaternion
q2 - Second component of the rotation quaternion
q3 - Third component of the rotation quaternion
q4 - Fourth component of the rotation quaternion
quality - Value between 0 and 1 defining the tracking quality. (1=tracking, 0=not tracking)
cosID - the coordinate system ID
cosName - Name of the coordinate system.
